<title>SOUTH AFRICA: LeisureNet takes 50 pct of schools group.</title>
<headline>LeisureNet takes 50 pct of schools group.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>LeisureNet Ltd said on Wednesday it had acquired an effective 50 percent interest in Crawford Education Holdings (Pty) Ltd for a maximum consideration of 32 million rand.</p>
<p>Crawford runs schools in the Johannesburg area.</p>
<p>The effective date of the deal is January 1, 1996.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
